{"tid":1478894,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[和平獎提名]  做左少少資料整合, 你都可以令香港人攞諾貝爾獎!","createTime":"2019-08-16T16:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T19:55:19.000Z","uid":155462,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"68a879e41da893182a57bd999cd5cab1ee9ea2b4","tid":1478894,"uid":155462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:39:09.000Z","msg":"長話短說: 我地係無辦法去提名既, 但我地可以叫有資格提名既人幫手提名<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n諾貝爾和平獎提名資格有幾個, 以下係最有可能幫到手既資格<br />\n<br />\n&bull;主權國家的現任元首、政府、官員、內閣成員及國會議員<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即係美國國會議員, 同英國國會議員都有資格！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n&bull;大學歷史、社會科學、法學、哲學、神學及宗教學科的教授、榮譽教授及副教授；大學校長及總監(或同級)；和平研究所或外交研究所的所長<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如字面意思, 你讀緊個間U既教授, 校長, 都有資格！[red]</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red]提名Deadline：2020年2月1日 零時</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n完整提名資格請睇:<a href=\"https://www.nobelpeaceprize.org/Nomination/Nominator-application-form\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nobelpeaceprize.org%2FNomination%2FNominator-application-form&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=55296963\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nobelpeaceprize.org/Nomination/Nominator-application-form</a><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n即係點做?即係以聯署, 共開呼籲等既方式向以上兩種人施壓同請願, 希望佢地可以提名香港人去攞呢個獎<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一步</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n草擬出電郵, 或聲明, 俾人去聯署。需要既係精通英文用國際文件既巴絲打, 例如攬炒巴打或者其他出到力既人。我先唔係度獻醜先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二步</span></span></strong><br />\n集合有提名資格人士既聯絡, 我係整左少少<br />\n<br />\n美國國會議員:佩羅茜議員(Ms Nancy Pelosi)<br />\n電郵:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speaker.gov/contact/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speaker.gov%2Fcontact%2F&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=a09451ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speaker.gov/contact/</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpeakerPelosi&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=690350fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NancyPelosi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNancyPelosi%2F&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=c88f453a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NancyPelosi/</a><br />\n<br />\n直接寄實體信去佢白宮Office:<br />\n1236 Longworth H.O.B.<br />\nWashington, DC 20515<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">背景: 陳雲係原Post中點名提及</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n美國國會議員:魯比奧議員(Mr Marco Rubio)<br />\n電郵:<a href=\"https://www.rubio.senate.gov/public/index.cfm/contact\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rubio.senate.gov%2Fpublic%2Findex.cfm%2Fcontact&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=afcf5910\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rubio.senate.gov/public/index.cfm/contact</a><br />\n<br />\n直接寄實體信去佢白宮Office:<br />\n284 Russell Senate Office Building<br />\nWashington, DC 20510<br />\n<br />\nTwitter:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=58c63929\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SenatorMarcoRubio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSenatorMarcoRubio&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=29db8aaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SenatorMarcoRubio</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">背景: 當年發起12個議員提名當時佔中三子去攞2018既和平獎, 亦係佢提出「香港人權與民主法案（Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Bill)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n美國國會及行政當局  中國委員會（CECC）主席 Mr. Christopher Smith<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Smith4NJ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSmith4NJ%2F&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=b5f14ac2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Smith4NJ/</a><br />\nEmail:info@smith4nj.com<br />\n地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />O Box 3184 Hamilton, NJ 08619<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">背景:係美國政府中專屌中國, 2018佢都有份提名<br />\n<br />\n「去年3月，史密夫於與魯比奧的聯合聲明中曾指，如果香港在特首林鄭月娥領導下淪為中國大陸另一個城市，美國需重新評估香港是否仍依照美國法律享有特權。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n至於附合「大學歷史、社會科學、法學、哲學、神學及宗教學科的教授、榮譽教授及副教授；大學校長及總監(或同級)；和平研究所或外交研究所的所長」既人............<br />\n<br />\n...實在太多, 唔一一整合了, 希望讀緊U既巴絲可以採取行動向佢地施壓, 希望佢地會提名<br />\n<br />\n香港大學歷史系教授們既聯絡資料同電郵:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www4.hku.hk/hkumcd/index.php/cht/unit/81_Department_of_History\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww4.hku.hk%2Fhkumcd%2Findex.php%2Fcht%2Funit%2F81_Department_of_History&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=a1f03f38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www4.hku.hk/hkumcd/index.php/cht/unit/81_Department_of_History</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n最後一步, 就當然係將之前既信同咩方式都瘋狂SEND出！<br />\n<br />\n當然你亦可以唔等範文, 用自己既文字Send 信寄信, 比起量產既文, 自己既文字可能更易打動! 試下手寫? 試下寄實體信? 前線巴打連速龍隊都唔驚, 又使乜驚自己英文廢?<br />\n<br />\n任何事係實現前都會覺得無可能!<br />\n但係我地係唔認輸既香港人!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1d9a53015fe45ea0c19edde52b6df5e0a2f09859","tid":1478894,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:39:28.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n保護自己資產，全民唱美元現鈔！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478882</a>"},{"pid":"0e9b0e1967ff058bb8bbd14187818f410aa56edd","tid":1478894,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7dc915658de28007056f0763c9ea229a2e5a64","tid":1478894,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:41:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6669a8f8e1f1d088c971ba78bb91751a267c676f","tid":1478894,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"為港爭光"},{"pid":"166cf5a674235c01974c407f88a19d29e55ba346","tid":1478894,"uid":155462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">WHATEVER IT TAKES</span></strong>"},{"pid":"094a54b2d055e1cdf49636aa862b482470069d8b","tid":1478894,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:49:02.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"3d5ec69b691fcda926c5ec959c976a2a0cc99b75","tid":1478894,"uid":155462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:51:24.000Z","msg":"美國國會及行政當局 中國委員會（CECC）主席 Mr. Christopher Smith<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Smith4NJ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSmith4NJ%2F&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=b5f14ac2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Smith4NJ/</a><br />\nEmail:info@smith4nj.com<br />\n地址: PO Box 3184 Hamilton, NJ 08619<br />\n<br />\n變左ICON <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a167d23bab30d895ff969e65c1a9b6963dd3193b","tid":1478894,"uid":155462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r